{"tid":595674,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每日自推","createTime":"2018-03-17T01:39:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T13:50:28.000Z","uid":78827,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb23d0db789772aa615c9c4b77de25789b3b542","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T01:39:14.000Z","msg":"希望唔算洗版"},{"pid":"7a8f6906f5fb7ff1d9d27506d94cd8feb3b79bde","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"自推一下<br />\n<br />\n吾生也有涯，而知也無涯。<br />\n以有涯隨無涯，殆已。"},{"pid":"f92a6865dc8f6dc5c956aa7f290ec46b14486b95","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:31:41.000Z","msg":"自推一下<br />\n<br />\n命運，其實係咪掌握o係自己手上？"},{"pid":"1c3e4fda0187a37799926cb749fc2b075d58b987","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-20T07:54:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n身體同心靈，其實密不可分"},{"pid":"34749abd20aecab0bc5d7e30792076d9fb48b836","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T02:12:48.000Z","msg":"21/3<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n平等，會唔會只係想R著數果時用既籍口？"},{"pid":"54212a9d8d82452aa32a42a292e8996440b23412","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T01:43:22.000Z","msg":"22/3<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n其實人大左，性格係咪就改變唔到？<br />\n即使係小朋友，出世冇耐其實已經睇到性格既唔同。<br />\n<br />\n有好動，有好靜；有愛笑，有愛哭；有主動，有被動；有外向，有內向...<br />\n<br />\n但透過後天既影響，包括家庭，親友，教育，工作環境等，係咪可以大程度地去改變一個人既性格呢？<br />\n<br />\n我既諗法係覺得有可能既，一方面可能係我既wishful thinking，另外係因為我相信大腦係一樣幾活潑既野，思維模式經過培養其實可以改變。<br />\n<br />\n現時所謂改唔到既性格，原因上係因為o係放任既環境下，不斷地自我加強而得黎。"},{"pid":"9e0940dbacfd7b0c5580e735cb9ff57af5bb95e1","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"23/3<br />\n<br />\n群體與個體<br />\n<br />\n群體與個體的行為/特徵是可以有很大差異的<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\nA={a,b,c} vs a, b, c<br />\n公司 vs 老闆/員工<br />\n政黨 vs 黨員<br />\n<br />\n以下集中討論人既群體與個體<br />\n<br />\n對於人既行為同特徵，所用以描述既詞彙係常見及容易理解既，例如：喜歡、討厭、強、弱、高、矮、不滿、...，呢d詞彙都容易讓人感同身受。<br />\n<br />\n而對於群體既行為同特徵，描述既方式就有所不同，若群體內每一個體之某一特徵相同時，使用該描述還可以接受，然而當某特徵於群體內不一致時，用描述個體既詞彙去描述群體會有所限制。例如中國人群體中有些人有禮貌，有些人沒有，此時不論說中國人是有禮貌還是沒有禮物都不合宜。<br />\n<br />\n..."},{"pid":"e7ead7ff25a0868c316d155adb2064843ac81b9f","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T16:46:55.000Z","msg":"24/3<br />\n<br />\nDo we live in a holographic universe?"},{"pid":"2375c8158afcf4de204b0df635f261b2dc145064","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:52:52.000Z","msg":"25/3<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n心志強壯，難免看起來無情"},{"pid":"68c713a2cd6b2f271fc5904428edbeccf2b01e90","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"26/3<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n建立一套習慣好有用，因為可以省卻好多猶豫既時間同精神。同埋自律係好費心神。"},{"pid":"1f37358da97d922add22d00cbd629c7a6b39b8b9","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T01:08:32.000Z","msg":"27/3<br />\n<br />\n今日，毛記"},{"pid":"cc9a80bbde22ccd8141a44d027bfc81261668141","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:26:59.000Z","msg":"28/3<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n今日都係毛記，不過淨係睇。<br />\n<br />\n識玩既人未必係好叻，但係要o係自己既領域知進退。<br />\n<br />\nLife is hard. Die hard .<br />\n<br />\n希望在明天"},{"pid":"840168593532d0bd3fe4e3734ca41970969105a5","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T17:16:10.000Z","msg":"29/3<br />\n<br />\nA complicated day"},{"pid":"3d6dee42e6ab083c181acffbcedbefc6f99cc127","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T01:44:58.000Z","msg":"30/3<br />\n<br />\n受苦節，受苦"},{"pid":"0de31f14c45d62dfc95d7896de9326fc790c20ac","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T17:51:15.000Z","msg":"31/3<br />\n<br />\n無常"},{"pid":"884a72c9abffd0ce7656e97eb3f885cb235eb8c6","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"1/4<br />\n<br />\n推<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女朋友<br />\n<br />\n尋日同女朋友講今日會去搵佢，今朝whatsapp佢知我攰攰地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一陣過黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你攰就唔好黎啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔緊要啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實我唔想你黎，你可以做下自己野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇呀唔緊要呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好啦，其實今日唔見都得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者我夜晚搵你食飯？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好啦，我今日想早d返屋企<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者我地食個飯之後咪早d返屋企<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好啦又特登出黎食個飯又返去，你今日留o係屋企啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係我知你都想見我wor<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ok啦你攰休息下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ok😘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後佢就嬲左我，話我應承左既野冇做。<br />\n<br />\n#愚人節快樂"},{"pid":"3761d119b97ba5beeb1ded09bff4782e7dcd7e9d","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:31:56.000Z","msg":"2/4<br />\n<br />\n開心<br />\n<br />\n佛系"},{"pid":"ad8c59b7555fcaa76c29e717e9519f6343e8101c","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"3/4<br />\n4/4<br />\n<br />\n終於真係斷左<br />\n<br />\n真係唔想自己做乜都冇恆心"},{"pid":"52b5ec64f3431ff0c704914cfd0fc866fb3fb06b","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-05T17:13:59.000Z","msg":"5/4 <br />\n<br />\n搞乜鬼，好亂"},{"pid":"25b7d221d784876a142b68c96261da2f55314b06","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T03:18:47.000Z","msg":"6/6 推<br />\n<br />\n點樣可以搵到神？"},{"pid":"1bf349dfea121bfdded4cb07d5f150b74a6353cc","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T13:29:45.000Z","msg":"7 8 9/3<br />\n<br />\n病到一個點"},{"pid":"033bc42ae77ede347dc8a5757472b90718b5a8bb","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"10/4<br />\n<br />\n病到連日期都錯埋"},{"pid":"17d25896d328585ba035ef2676525333ad7056d9","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T13:36:27.000Z","msg":"神啊<br />\n求你憐憫我<br />\n解除我既痛苦"},{"pid":"26222ea0ec5d19d255842a2be79b0acc5a5f3982","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T16:05:40.000Z","msg":"11/4<br />\n<br />\n祈禱"},{"pid":"5394e6aea8f9a3029bc22bd2b0227ef542cba890","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:08:37.000Z","msg":"12/4<br />\n<br />\n心好像成長了"},{"pid":"3c0462957a76ce6baf224e137ee87d204c8f3a7c","tid":595674,"uid":73650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:48:17.000Z","msg":"加油巴打"},{"pid":"f2efc8e644cb175a611b8fc5fef64504ee7e8893","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"13/4<br />\n<br />\n終於有人回#tongue3<br />\n<br />\n念念不忘，必有回響"},{"pid":"6618b83ffc14520963130732def04e9f37be7400","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T02:44:25.000Z","msg":"14/4<br />\n<br />\n病足一