al/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都似乎搵到要追逐既信仰啦"},{"pid":"370e84fa6eefcc1a95f102c9014b022fc211c613","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"22/5<br />\n<br />\n正所謂<br />\n念念不忘，必有回響。<br />\n<br />\n我咁做其實係想累積一點點既力量，<br />\n或者有一日睇返，會成為激勵。<br />\n<br />\n做人，不求面面俱圓，只求對得住天地良心。<br />\n唔好太著意追逐世界既標準，人地既期望。<br />\n自己既人生，唔需要靠人地既肯定先有價值。"},{"pid":"afed20eab70702fe12becb1369c589322696eb3f","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"23/5<br />\n<br />\n好努力<br />\n但力不從心<br />\n<br />\n好想做好，但都只係一廂情願。<br />\n<br />\n要成為leader，仲有好遠既路。<br />\n<br />\n多謝一路同行既戰友。"},{"pid":"4473e98c9abe2bb8918f7e960ae120fd24535f75","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"24/5<br />\n<br />\nA little milestone<br />\n<br />\n睇返，其實可能只係白忙<br />\n<br />\n又或者，好似做運動咁。<br />\n<br />\n到最後，只係剩返變強既自己。"},{"pid":"20fb95f5f6d20a24a48ea28c5cd65e0c2e25fc70","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T11:37:28.000Z","msg":"25/5<br />\n<br />\n今日見識到d高層既鐵腕<br />\n係厲害既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nI Pray<br />\nCoz I know the power of prayer."},{"pid":"4ee8c517b258293af08568aa4fc2c3bd6ab5edb0","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"26/5<br />\n<br />\n簡簡單單，不過不失"},{"pid":"45de182714116693d215b076d54ffd8805136f95","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"27/5<br />\n<br />\nTime flies."},{"pid":"ec2eeb96427537fa7bfdb152bb3165e0509ba5f3","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T12:21:08.000Z","msg":"28/5<br />\n<br />\n終於..."},{"pid":"027f5d06e83fc590cc2f37030196aadb10f02827","tid":595674,"uid":78827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T